analysis.reasoning: Algorithm A returns a higher proportion of actual mid-motor e-bikes in the top results, showing a variety of full-bike listings and recognizable consumer models (Vogue, Altec, Puch, SachsenRAD). Top slots in A are relevant to the query, include popular models and visible price/compare labels that help user value decisions. Algorithm B surfaces more non-bike items (chains/chainrings/accessory packaging) and repeats identical product images among the top slots, which reduces relevance and immediate user value for someone searching specifically for “E-bike met Middenmotor.”
